 are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Gobert d'Aspremont IV was born about 1115, in Verdun, Meuse, Grand Est, France, his father, Gobert III seigneur d`Aspremont, was 32 and his mother, Hadwige de Joinville, was 22. He married Adélaïde de Dun in 1140. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 2 daughters. He died in 1163, at the age of 49."},"et":{"Abt 1115–1163":"umbes 1115–1163","1115–1163":"1115–1163","1120–Female":"1120–Surnud","1120–1163":"1120–1163","1140–Female":"1140–Surnud","1142–1190":"1142–1190","1145–1207":"1145–1207","1085–1138":"1085–1138","1094–1141":"1094–1141","1190":"1190","1142":"1142","1120":"1120","Abt 1115":"umbes 1115","1163":"1163","1141":"1141","1140":"1140","1085":"1085","1094":"1094","Abt 1163":"umbes 1163","1138":"1138","1115":"1115","um 1142":"umbes 1142","ABT 1145":"umbes 1145","1145":"1145","após 1141":"pärast 1141","1207":"1207","Aspremont, Verdun-sur-Meuse, Meuse, Kingdom of France":"Verdun, Meuse, Grand Est, Prantsusmaa","Verdun-sur-Meuse, Meuse, Lorraine, Frankrijk":"Verdun, Meuse, Lorraine, Prantsusmaa","Chiny":"Hiina"},"fi":{"Abt 1115–1163":"noin 1115–1163","1115–1163":"1115–1163","1120–Female":"1120–Kuollut","1120–1163":"1120–1163","1140–Female":"1140–Kuollut","1142–1190":"1142–1190","1145–1207":"1145–1207","1085–1138":"1085–1138","1094–1141":"1094–1141","1190":"1190","1142":"1142","1120":"1120","Abt 1115":"noin 1115","1163":"1163","1141":"1141","1140":"1140","1085":"1085","1094":"1094","Abt 1163":"noin 1163","1138":"1138","1115":"1115","um 1142":"noin 1142","ABT 1145":"noin 1145","1145":"1145","após 1141":"1141 jälkeen","1207":"1207","Aspremont, Verdun-sur-Meuse, Meuse, Kingdom of France":"Verdun, Meuse, Grand Est, Ranska","Verdun-sur-Meuse, Meuse, Lorraine, Frankrijk":"Verdun, Meuse, Lorraine, Ranska","Chiny":"Kiina"},"fr":{"Abt 1115–1163":"environ 1115–1163","1115–1163":"1115–1163","1120–Female":"1120–Décédée","1120–1163":"1120–1163","1140–Female":"1140–Décédée","1142–1190":"1142–1190","114